
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Personal_life">Personal life</span></h2>

<p>In 1992, Nadella married Anupama, daughter of his father's <a
            href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Indian_Administrative_Service" title="Indian Administrative Service">Indian
        Administrative Service</a> (IAS) batchmate, K.R. Venugopal.<sup id="cite_ref-33" class="reference"><a
                href="#cite_note-33">[33]</a></sup> The families had known each other
    for thirty years and the marriage was arranged by their parents. The couple have three children, a son and two
    daughters, and live in <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bellevue,_Washington" title="Bellevue, Washington">Bellevue,
        Washington</a>.<sup id="cite_ref-POLITICO_04FEB14_4-1" class="reference"><a
                href="#cite_note-POLITICO_04FEB14-4">[4]</a></sup><sup
            id="cite_ref-34" class="reference"><a
                href="#cite_note-34">[34]</a></sup></p>

